    File: ParcelConditionScript.java
   
    Accela, Inc.
    Copyright (C): 2001-2014
   
    Description:
    Provides the "aa.parcelCondition" object through which script writers can
    operate on an retrieve ParcelCondition related objects.
   
    Notes:
   
   
    Revision History:
    01/18/2002, jlu,         Initial Version
    02/26/02    CherryYang   Added getParcelConditions through the ParcelCondition(all members)
                             Add one method: getOneRWC(ParcelConditionModel pcroc)
    05/11/02     jlu         remove two methods added by Cherry due to script security.
                             remove parameter sourceNumber, and use service provider's code only in API
    12/17/02            Owen Yang   Add three methods:
                                                                AddParcelCondition(ParcelConditionScriptModel parcelCondition);
                                                                UpdateParcelCondition(ParcelConditionScriptModel parcelCondition, long conditionID, long  parcelID);
                                                                DeleteParcelCondition(long conditionID, long parcelID)
